<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW -- Russia is to issue a 500,000- ruble (about 88
U.S. dollars at current rate) bank note - its largest ever - next
week, an official said Friday.
</P>
<P>
NEW DELHI -- The United Front government places priority on
science and technology in the new budget for 1997-98 which
doubles its allocation fund over the previous fiscal year,
Finance Minister P. Chidambaram said Friday.
</P>
<P>
