evening, proposed to increase three billion rupees (84.51 million
US dollars) for the country's science and technology sector.
</P>
<P>
BONN -- German Foreign Minister Klaus Kinkel Friday floated the
idea to limit the stationing of conventional weapon systems in
east European candidate countries in a bid to ease Russia's
concerns over the NATO eastward expansion.
</P>
