<HEADLINE> Malaria Kills 200 Zimbabweans in Two Months </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, February 28 (Xinhua) -- Malaria has claimed 201 lives
in Zimbabwe since January with a total 106,721 cases reported
countrywide.
</P>
<P>
