chopping off hands or legs of the armed bandits in accordance
with Islamic Sharia law were displayed at the meeting.
</P>
<P>
Armed men frequently carry out armed banditry and kill
commuters in the areas inhabited by the Galjel clan along the
road to the central regions. Hence the establishment of the
Islamic courts to cope with the situation. 
