<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, February 28 (Xinhua) -- Two people were killed and
six police officers and at least two bystanders were wounded in a
battle between a gang of bank robbers and police officers in Los
Angeles today.
</P>
<P>
The masked robbers, wearing body armor and carrying automatic
military rifles started to rob a Bank of America branch in North
Hollywood at about 9 a.m. local time. When police arrived, the
robbers started to shoot at the policemen with AK-47s and AR-15s.
</P>
<P>
