and two citizens were wounded in the battle which ended at noon.
</P>
<P>
After the battle, police were entering the bank to rescue
people who locked themselves in the vault during the robbery.
</P>
<P>
The manhunt for the remaining robbers spread out through North
Hollywood, about 10 miles west of downtown Los Angeles.
</P>
<P>
Hours after the battle, the neighborhood was still declared a
dangerous area and police warned the public to either stay away or
stay inside and lock their doors. 
