<HEADLINE> Hu Jintao on Social Stability, National Unity and Ethnic Solidarity (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics and the Party's basic line are absolutely
correct, so are all major decisions and arrangements made by the
Party Central Committee with Jiang Zemin at the core for promoting
the great cause of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics, including a series of instructions and principles
on work for Tibet," he noted.
</P>
<P>
He went on to say that the Chinese people should unswervingly
adhere to the fundamental theories, basic line and principles of
the Party, work hard to promote economic development, and firmly
safeguard social stability, to welcome Hong Kong's return and the
15th Party national congress with deeds.
</P>
<P>
Before Hu spoke, deputies discussed the government work report
delivered by Premier Li Peng at this morning's opening ceremony of
the current NPC session, and praised it for making a comprehensive
and objective summary of last year's work and reflecting the
spirit of seeking truth from facts.
</P>
<P>
The deputies said that they will hold high the banner of Deng
Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics, and perform their duties well under the
leadership of the Party Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin
at the core to contribute their share to the development of Tibet.
</P>
