Pakistan "to investigate attack on the Iranian Cultural Center in
Multan," east of Pakistan's Punjab province on February 20.
</P>
<P>
The spokesman, however, denied the reports, saying that "no
team from Iran is visiting Pakistan for the purpose of
investigation."
</P>
<P>
The spokesman said that during his stay here Sarmadi is
expected to hold talks with high ranking Pakistani government
officials on the tragic Multan incident in which an Iranian
official and six other Pakistanis were killed.  
