<HEADLINE> NPC Fifth Session Opens  (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The 17,000-word work report comprises seven parts, on
respectively: review of government work in domestic affairs in
1996; maintaining a good momentum of growth in the national
economy in 1997; making great strides in reforming state-owned
enterprises; taking the initiative to develop science, technology,
education, culture and other social undertakings; consolidating
and developing social and political unity and stability; ensuring
a smooth transfer of government and a smooth transition in Hong
Kong and promoting a peaceful reunification of the motherland; and
diplomatic work.
</P>
<P>
At the end of his report, Li said that the Chinese people will
turn grief into strength, carry on with their work at the behest
of Deng Xiaoping and, under the leadership of the Party Central
Committee with Jiang Zemin at the core and keeping in mind the
country's fundamental interests, advance in a pioneering spirit to
further the great cause initiated by Deng, and achieve new
successes in reform, opening up and socialist modernization.
</P>
