has international support, especially about the final status of
autonomous Palestine," the statement said.
</P>
<P>
On Wednesday, a Ministerial Committee of Israel endorsed an
agreement on establishing 6,500 housing units for the Jewish
settlers in East Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
"Indonesia calls on the U.N. Security Council to take steps to
cancel the Israeli government's decision to build the Jewish
settlement," it added.
</P>
<P>
Indonesia, home of the world's largest Muslim population and a
founder of the Non-Aligned Movement, have long been a firm
supporter of the Palestinian cause.  
