<HEADLINE> French Ougier Wins Dual Moguls in Freestyle Skiing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, February 28 (Xinhua) -- Fabrice Ougier of France won
the men's dual mogul freestyle skiing in Meiringen Hasliberg,
Switzerland on Friday.
</P>
<P>
Sweden's Jonas Jonell finished second, chased by Russian Sergei
Karpetchenko. World champion Jean-Luc Brassard finished back in
fifth.
</P>
