women's event wherein Minna Karhu of Finland ranked second.
</P>
<P>
World champion Candice Gilg of France finished a distant
fifth.
</P>
<P>
The dual moguls kicked off a weekend of World Cup freestyle
skiing in the Swiss resort. 
