regions have applied to attend the fair, and some countries'
ambassadors to China will be invited to the event, the officials
said.
</P>
<P>
Hi-tech products, machinery and electronics, and business talks
on technological co-operation are expected to play a leading role
during the eight-day event, the biggest one ever to be held in
this metropolis.
</P>
<P>
The fair, jointly launched by Beijing, Tianjin and ten
provinces and autonomous regions in northern and western parts of
the country, has become a key foreign trade activity in north
China.  
